text: Yousry or Yousri () is an Arabic given name and surname. Notable people with this name include: ==Given name== ===Yousri=== *Yousri Belgaroui, Dutch- Tunisian kickboxer ===Yousry=== *Yousry Nasrallah (born 1952), Egyptian film director *Yousry Saber Hussein El-Gamal, Egyptian politician and government minister *Yousry Zagloul (born 1954), Egyptian judoka *Yousry Ibrahim Farag (born 1952), Egyptian Projects Manager , Civil Engineer ==Surname== ===Yousri=== * Madiha Yousri, Egyptian actress * Mohamed Yousri Salama, Egyptian politician * Nahed Yousri, Egyptian actress ===Yousry=== * Amina Yousry, Egyptian squash player * Mohamed Yousry, Egyptian interpreter ==See also== *Yousra, feminine of Yousri / Yousry
title: Yousry
